  "description": "Casa La Maestranza is a fully refurbished 3-bed apartment; exquisitely decorated, offering elegant functionality - all you'd expect from a holiday home.\n\nThe open-plan kitchen-living area provides a stylish space to relax and dine. This is continued on the terrace which features outdoor dining furniture and a Weber gas BBQ… perfect for Summer Alfresco Dining. The kitchen offers modern appliances (including a dishwasher and washing machine) and all the necessary equipment.\n\nThe Master bedroom has a beautiful ensuite bathroom featuring two rain showers and has access to the terrace. There are a further 2 bedrooms (one double and one twin) and a shared bathroom.\n\nThere is hot/cold air conditioning, International television, WIFI, and a parking space in the garage.\n\nThis apartment offers a fresh, contemporary, and stylish space to enjoy your holidays…. an absolute gem!\n\nSet in the heart of Nueva Andalucia, surrounded by amenities (supermarket, butcher and wine shop just round the corner), a very short distance to Marbella’s finest Golf Clubs, and only a 20-minute walk to the beach and Puerto Banús: La Maestranza boasts a fantastic location. Add to that several communal swimming pools (one heated!) and tropical gardens, this urbanisation is perfect for a holiday in Marbella.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you.",
